#: ../../modules/readout/readout.rst:242
msgid "Intermediate Results"
msgstr "Resultados Intermedios"

#: ../../modules/readout/readout.rst:244
msgid ""
"When a functional is constructed with ``store_intermediate_results=True``"
" (currently supported by :class:`~qilisdk.functionals.AnalogEvolution` "
"and :class:`~qilisdk.functionals.QuantumReservoir`), the backend stores a"
" readout result for every time step.  The same readout methods apply at "
"each step."
msgstr ""
"Cuando un funcional se construye con ``store_intermediate_results=True`` "
"(actualmente compatible con :class:`~qilisdk.functionals.AnalogEvolution` "
"y :class:`~qilisdk.functionals.QuantumReservoir`), el backend almacena un "
"resultado de lectura para cada paso temporal. Los mismos métodos de lectura "
"se aplican en cada paso."

